cnova  wikipedia cnova from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search cnova nv type public traded as nasdaq cnv industry ecommerce founded  headquarters amsterdam netherlands and sao paulo brazil key people jeancharles naouri ceo and chairman revenue  billion euros  number of employees   website cnovagroupcomen cnova nv is an ecommerce company founded in june  cnova includes cdiscount operating in france belgium ivory coast senegal and colombia and cnova brazil operating in brazil cnova nv is part of groupe casino a french global retail company of which mr jeancharles naouri is currently the chairman and ceo since november  peter paul estermann is the chairman of the board of cnova nv in  the total sales of cnova nv reached  billion euros and its total revenue reached  billion euros at the end of  cnova counted  million active customers in the world contents  history  presentation  subsidiaries  cdiscount  cnova brazil  management  executive committee  references  external links historyedit the first operations began in  with the founding of the ecommerce website cdiscount a single website focused on offering cds and dvds cdiscount then expanded its business to encompass product categories such as consumer electronics computers home appliances and wine in  the companies pontofriocom and ehub were launched in brazil providing ecommerce services to thirdparty retailers the brazilian expansion continued in  by adding the extracombr and casasbahiacombr websites to the portfolio and the creation of business unit focused on businesstobusiness wholesale called pontofrio atacado in  cdiscount implemented its first marketplace and launched comptoirsantecom an ecommerce website dedicated to beauty products during the year  two new websites were launched in brazil an online marketplace was also created on the extracombr website in brazil  cnova a global ecommerce company with a total gross merchandise volume of  billion was created through a joint venture between casino gpa via varejo and exito cnova will be directly owned  by casino including its subsidiary exito and  indirectly by gpa via varejo and certain founding shareholders of nova pontocom  saw the merger of both french and brazilian ecommerce activities under the cnova umbrella as well as the cdiscount expansion in colombia ivory coast belgium and senegal presentationedit the current geographies represent over  million people with cnova sites in france brazil colombia ivory coast belgium and senegal and operations in brazil under the sites extracombr pontofriocom and casasbahiacombr it operates bb solutions such as the ecommerce solution ehub and niche sites both in france and brazil with comptoirsantecom moncornerdecocom or barateirocom cnova has established itself as an ecommerce market leader in france and brazil through the direct sales websites and its marketplaces cnova offers an extensive product assortment including home appliances consumer electronics computers home furnishings leisure and personal goods and differentiated delivery and payment options subsidiariesedit cdiscountedit cdiscount is a french company created in  it has been part of casino group since  as the first ecommerce website in france cdiscount offers a wide range of products including among others cultural goods hightech it household appliances personal appliances and food cdiscount also operates in brazil belgium ivory coast senegal and colombia in  cdiscount employed  people and had a turnover of  billion euros cnova braziledit cnova brazil is specialized in ecommerce activities throughout the country its creation follows the merger of the online activities of casas bahia ponto frio and extra a hypermarket chain belonging to the brazilian group pão de açúcar the leading national retailer in brazil cnova brazil structures its ecommerce services through three main bc websites – extracombr casasbahiacombr and pontofriocom – as well as bb services through pontofrio atacado and its ehub platform cnova brazil is a major ecommerce player in brazil with a turnover of  billion euros in  managementedit executive committeeedit emmanuel grenier ceo and executive director of cnova stéphane brunel chief financial officer of cnova and cdiscount referencesedit  a b cnova  le chiffre daffaires de cdiscount en légère progression lsa conso  march   cnova board changes reuters  november   cnova investors presentation cnovacom february   cdiscount at the heart of b to b ecommerce deliver  france  january   company overview of pontofriocom investing businessweek  october   cdiscount lancera en juin une eboutique de lentilles de contact journal du net  may   casino guichard perrachon sets up with via varejo global ecommerce joint venture cnova reuters  june  retrieved  june   casino group creation of a major global ecommerce  cnova globenewswire  june  retrieved  june   casino group creation of a major global ecommerce – cnova euroinvestor  june   casino files to float ecommerce unit cnova in new york wall street journal – online  june   alibaba ipo timing bodes well for casinos cnova listing cnbc  september   casino lance « cnova » sa société mondiale de ecommerce les echos  june   company overview of cnova nv blommberg businessweek  october   cdiscount premier ecommerçant de france journal du net  june   cdiscount  groupe casino groupecasinocom  cnova brazil a major ecommerce player in brazil groupe casino  cnova nv  nv   activité de lexercice  zone bourse  january   cnv profile yahoo finance  external linksedit official website cdiscount website nova pontocom website internet portal companies portal retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlecnovaoldid categories cnovacommerce websitesdutch brandscompanies listed on nasdaqhidden categories use dmy dates from november pages using infobox company with unsupported parameters navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view his