oup since  as the first ecommerce website in france cdiscount offers a wide range of products including among others cultural goods hightech it household appliances personal appliances and food cdiscount also operates in brazil belgium ivory coast senegal and colombia in  cdiscount employed  people and had a turnover of  billion euros cnova braziledit cnova brazil is specialized in ecommerce activities throughout the country its creation follows the merger of the online activities of casas bahia ponto frio and extra a hypermarket chain belonging to the brazilian group pão de açúcar the leading national retailer in brazil cnova brazil structures its ecommerce services through three main bc websites – extracombr casasbahiacombr and pontofriocom – as well as bb services through pontofrio atacado and its ehub platform cnova brazil is a major ecommerce player in brazil with a turnover of  billion euros in  managementedit executive committeeedit emmanuel grenier ceo and executive director of cnova stéphane brunel chief financial officer of cnova and cdiscount referencesedit  a b cnova  le chiffre daffaires de cdiscount en légère progression lsa conso  march   cnova board changes reuters  november   cnova investors presentation cnovacom february   cdiscount at the heart of b to b ecommerce deliver  france  january   company overview of pontofriocom investing businessweek  october   cdiscount lancera en juin une eboutique de lentilles de contact journal du net  may   casino guichard perrachon sets up with via varejo global ecommerce joint venture cnova reuters  june  retrieved  june   casino group creation of a major global ecommerce  cnova globenewswire  june  retrieved  june   casino group creation of a major global ecommerce – cnova euroinvestor  june   casino files to float ecommerce unit cnova in new york wall street journal – online  june   alibaba ipo timing bodes well for casinos cnova listing cnbc  september   casino lance « cnova » sa société mondiale de ecommerce