customers  million  cdav subscribers       orders  million  cdav share                      bp launch of volumecentric strategic realignment cdiscount renews market share gains gfk emmanuel grenier cnova ceo commented during the nd quarter of  our traffic and gmv grew at a doubledigit rates our customer loyalty program doubled in size and our marketplace accounted for more than onethird of our gmv it is clear to us that thanks to our technological expertise we have one of the best traffic growth dynamics in france and our mission going forward is to leverage this into higher gmv and net sales growth rates on a sustainable basis to do this we have embarked on a new strategic realignment plan designed to one expand massively our direct sales product range two reinforce our multichannel offer and three accelerate the introduction of new bb revenue streams cdiscount is entering into a new growth phase which will see compared to the end of  its direct sales product range nearly quadruple in size a  increase of its marketplace product catalogue and an  expansion of its distribution center floor space by the end of the st quarter of  the new revenue streams we are introducing or accelerating will include increased marketplace fulfillment new bb services for our marketplace vendors such as foreign exchange and merchant financing new databased revenues consumer credit and insurance solutions and on top of all of this we are improving customer satisfaction before and after purchase for example we are launching a new multichannel strategy that includes a new delivery option and we are making more progress in terms of light product delivery speed we have completely revamped our mobile siteapplication and customer area to make it more reactive and to make ordering products easier and faster the implementation of these growth initiatives which temporarily weigh on margins and free cash flow this year will allow cdiscount to reinforce its top player status while strengthening its underlying profitability profile on a sustainable basis these strategic moves are already stimulating topline growth they also allow us to enter into new markets where we are making market share advances nd quarter  highlights gmv gross merchandise volume totaled € million an increase of  compared to the same period in  on a likeforlike lfl basis on a reported basis gmv rose  compared to  the mobile share of gmv was  representing a growth of  basis points the marketplace share of total gmv continue to expand reaching  for an increase of  basis points the number of products available increased by  the share of marketplace gmv fulfilled by cdiscount rose from  at the end of june  to  one year later while the number of vendors using cdiscounts fulfillment services doubled yoy the quality of our marketplace vendors showed continuous improvement with customer satisfaction up by  points on average since the beginning of  compared to last year    net sales totaled € million in the nd quarter  up  on a lfl basis compared to the same period in   on a reported basis home furnishings and household appliances accounted for  of direct sales while hitech items av and smartphones and it goods represented  of direct sales according to gfk may  cdiscounts technical goods hitech computers and home appliances value and volume market share grew yoy by  and  basis points respectively traffic at cdiscountcom during the nd quarter of  grew by  yearonyear yoy to  million visits traffic has grown on average by doubledigits on a yoy basis every quarter since the beginning of  according to médiamétrie cdiscount posted the highest progression among the five main eretailers in france during the first five months of  in terms of the number of desktop unique monthly visitors the mobile share of traffic increased  basis points to  during the same period and has been growing by an average of  basis points per quarter since the beginning of  traffic q q q q q q growth yoy       mobile share       th